{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_has_any_perk}}::1}}}}### Perk System
Perk: Traits, training, and peculiarities possessed by {{user}}. When representing a perk, it is better to express it indirectly rather than mentioning the name directly.

{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Lucky_Bastard_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Character) Strangely, minor luck seems to follow {{user}} in most endeavors.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Lucky_Coin_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Character) {{user}} somehow acquired 14 Ancient Empire gold coins that can no longer be obtained and kept them as lucky tokens. Current tokens remaining: {{getvar::cv_Lucky_Coin_Count}}{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Rabbit_Foot_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Character) Obtain a Rabbit's Foot through strange circumstances. It is a charm known to bring minor luck just by possessing it.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Preparation_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Character) As a meticulous planner, always fully prepared.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Beloved_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Character) Loved by women for various reasons. Naturally charming to them.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Promising_Youth_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Character) Older men (Lords, Jarls, Friars, etc.) tend to look favorably upon promising youths and offer their support.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Deft_Hands_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Melee) Actively utilizes the weapon's characteristics for technical fighting. Sword: Winding, crossguard binding, false edge cuts, half-swording, unorthodox Mordhau. Axe/Polearm: Hooking, haft strikes. Mace: Technical handling using wrist snaps.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Tempo_Melee_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Melee) Understands and utilizes the rhythm of combat, flowing with the tide of battle.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Combat_Training_Melee_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Melee) Possesses solid basics and fundamentals of combat.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Berserk_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Melee) A berserker who fights with overwhelming power, disregarding personal safety.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Footwork_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Melee) Blocks and deflects enemy attacks using nimble footwork and weapon parries. When failing a skill check and about to be hit, instead of taking immediate damage, a second skill check is offered. Damage is taken only if this second check also fails.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Bulwark_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Melee) Deflects and parries enemy attacks using weapons and armor. When failing a skill check and about to be hit, instead of taking immediate damage, a second skill check is offered. Damage is taken only if this second check also fails.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Vanguard_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Melee) Confronts enemies head-on, taking the front line to protect allies.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Swashbuckler_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Melee) Elusive on the battlefield, striking unpredictably from chaos rather than focusing on protection.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Veteran_Melee_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Melee) Calm in battle and not easily flustered, ensuring consistent performance.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Champion_Melee_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Melee) Renowned martial prowess.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Bullseye_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Marksmanship) Excellent eyesight and aim allow for difficult shots or ignoring cover.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Tempo_Archery_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Marksmanship) Understands and utilizes the rhythm of combat, flowing with the tide of battle.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Combat_Training_Archery_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Marksmanship) Possesses solid basics and fundamentals of archery.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Spray_and_Pray_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Marksmanship) Favors volume of fire over precise aiming.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Marksman_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Marksmanship) Prefers calculated shots that suppress and neutralize the enemy.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Skirmisher_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Marksmanship) Prefers tactics that harass and pressure the enemy continuously.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Second_Shot_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Marksmanship) Remain unfazed by a missed attack and attempt another shot to surely suppress the enemy. When failing a skill check and about to be hit, instead of taking immediate damage, a second skill check is offered. Damage is taken only if this second check also fails.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Tactical_Redeployment_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Marksmanship) Quickly repositions to safety when a shot misses its mark. When failing a skill check and about to be hit, instead of taking immediate damage, a second skill check is offered. Damage is taken only if this second check also fails.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Veteran_Archery_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Marksmanship) Calm in battle and not easily flustered, ensuring consistent performance.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Champion_Archery_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Marksmanship) Renowned prowess with the bow.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Toughness_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Athletics) Physically robust and unfazed by injuries during combat.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Indomitable_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Athletics) A sturdy physique and mental fortitude that inspires stability in allies.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Iron_Lungs_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Athletics) Possesses immense stamina that allows for prolonged exertion in combat.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Agile_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Athletics) Fast and light-footed. Can easily climb buildings or trees.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Unstoppable_Force_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Athletics) Incredibly strong. Can throw opponents larger than {{user}} or match their strength.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Low_Profile_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Stealth) Mastered the basics of staying hidden and avoiding detection.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Stealth_Training_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Stealth) Faithful to the fundamentals of stealth.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Master_of_Escape_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Stealth) When a stealth attempt fails, can use tools(eg. Smokebomb) or terrain to escape and re-attempt stealth.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Thiefs_Luck_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Stealth) Sometimes, pure luck intervenes in {{user}}'s favor.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Fearsome_Presence_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Stealth) Successful takedowns strike fear into nearby enemies.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Ranger_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Survival) At home in forests and alleys, skilled at pathfinding and tracking.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Insight_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Survival) Skilled at noticing signs, tracks, and weaknesses, and sharing this information with allies.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Hunter_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Survival) A skilled hunter whose experience translates into skill with the bow.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Animal_Whisperer_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Survival) Knowledge of wildlife allows communication with animals, calming or taming them.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Folk_Remedies_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Survival) Knows how to treat and care for wounds efficiently. Treated as having medical knowledge.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Trap_Expert_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Craftsmanship) Can utilize improvised or prepared traps effectively.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Handyman_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Craftsmanship) Excellent dexterity allows handling most tasks. Treated as an artisan such as a weaver, carpenter, or blacksmith.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Architect_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Craftsmanship) Thoroughly understands building structures. Can discover hidden routes.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Quartermaster_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Craftsmanship) Meticulously maintains companions' equipment, ensuring it performs at its peak. {{user}}'s gear is of exceptional quality.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Camaraderie_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Speech) Knows how to elicit help and cooperation from allies.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Basic_Speech_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Speech) Learned the fundamentals of persuasion, deception, and intimidation.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Orator_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Speech) Excellent rhetoric. Can argue logically and persuasively.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Loudmouth_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Speech) Excellent rhetoric. Overwhelms opponents with endless, verbose talking.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Silence_is_Gold_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Speech) Excellent rhetoric. Persuades others with concise words and impressive actions.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Intimidating_Presence_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Speech) Presence alone can be a means of persuasion or gaining trust, backed by martial prowess.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Womanizer_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Speech) Skilled at handling and charming women.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Snake_Tongue_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Speech) Can taunt or provoke opponents to create favorable situations.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Fast_Learner_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Scholarship) Learns and absorbs information quickly.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Basic_Scholarship_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Scholarship) Possesses the ability to read and write proficiently. In this world, merely having this level of literacy qualifies one as a person of common sense and intellect.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Tactician_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Scholarship) Knowledgeable in tactics and strategy. Can utilize allies effectively.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Medic_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Scholarship) Excellent in medicine. Manages allies' health and diet.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Alchemist_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Scholarship) Can create and use poisons, explosives, and enhancers to strengthen allies.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Martial_Scholar_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Scholarship) Deeply read in martial arts manuals. Applies academic knowledge to combat.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Jack_of_All_Trades_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Scholarship) A repository of miscellaneous knowledge applicable to various situations.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Lore_Master_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Scholarship) A walking history book. Possesses immense knowledge.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Magician_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Magic) Can read and manipulate the flow of Pneuma due to talent or learning.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Spell_Attunement_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Magic) Magic is stable and more precise.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Magic_Support_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Magic) Skilled at supporting allies with magic.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Arcane_Enlightenment_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Magic) Can directly feel and see the flow of Pneuma, providing insight even in mundane tasks.{{/if}}{{#if_pure {{equal::{{getvar::cv_Perk_Spell_Mastery_acquired}}::1}}}}
- (Magic) Renowned as a mage. Highly skilled in manipulating magic.{{/if}}{{/if}}
